<br>
AA points-Agree with you there, similiar amnts, hopefully in similiar areas.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ugamrok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gamrok</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 154<br> <font color=#333333>(5/31/02 12:00:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=225.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hmm.</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> If both sides have SOW (or JBoots, etc), enchanters will slightly edge out magicians in number of kills, but have 5-10 times as many deaths.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
